1. Created the directory 0x03-sass_scss inside the alx-intermediate-frontend repository.
2. Installed NVM (Node Version Manager) using:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
3. Closed and reopened the terminal.
4. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using:
   nvm install 20.16
5. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using:
   npm install sass -v 3.7.4
6. Verified the installation using:
   npx sass --version
